1. Please enter your email address, make a selection, and submit your request to save your preference. Please see the
Marriott Group U.S. Consumer Privacy Statement
for information about how Marriott Sells personal data as defined under the CPA.
Enter Your Email Address
Email Address
Make a Selection
Opt-Out of Sale: We will stop Selling the personal data associated with this email address only (if you have more than one account with us, you will need to submit a request for each account).
Opt Back Into Sale (if you have previously opted out): We will start Selling the personal data associated with this email address only (if you have more than one account with us, you will need to submit a request for each account).
SUBMIT YOUR REQUEST TO SAVE YOUR PREFERENCE
2.Please click on
Tracking Preferences
, select “Advertising Cookies” from the sidebar on the left-hand side, toggle the switch to the left, and select “Confirm My Choices.” This action will opt you out of Selling for the browser you are using. To opt back into Selling, please follow the same steps outlined above, but instead, toggle the switch to the right and select “Confirm My Choices.”
To opt-out of Targeted Advertising under the CPA, please complete both steps:
1.Please enter your email address, make a selection, and submit your request to save your preference.
Enter Your Email Address
Email Address
Make a Selection
Opt-Out of Targeted Advertising: We will opt you out of Targeted Advertising for the personal data associated with this email address only (if you have more than one account with us, you will need to submit a request for each account).
Opt Back Into Targeted Advertising (if you have previously opted out): We will opt you back into Targeted Advertising for the personal data associated with this email address only (if you have more than one account with us, you will need to submit a request for each account).
SUBMIT YOUR REQUEST TO SAVE YOUR PREFERENCE
2. Please click on
Tracking Preferences
, select “Advertising Cookies” from the sidebar on the left-hand side, toggle the switch to the left, and select “Confirm My Choices.” This action will opt you out of Targeted Advertising for the browser you are using. To opt back into Targeted Advertising, please follow the same steps outlined above, but instead, toggle the switch to the right and select “Confirm My Choices."
Opt-In to the Collection and Use of Sensitive Personal Data:
Marriott does not collect Sensitive personal data, as defined under the CPA, unless we obtain your opt-in consent.
Profiling:
Marriott does not engage in Profiling in furtherance of decisions that produce legal or similarly significant effects concerning consumers, as those terms are defined under the CPA.
All Other Rights:
To exercise all other rights under the CPA, such as the Right to Access, the Right to Delete, the Right to Correct, and the Right to Appeal, please visit the
Individual Rights Portal
.
