Universal Opt-Out:
Some browsers allow for a Universal Opt-out of Sale and Targeted Advertising. If you visit our site and you have chosen to limit these activities via a Universal Opt-out, that choice will override your Tracking Preferences choice on our site, and, if you are logged in, opt you out of both Selling and Targeted Advertising above. Please note that the Universal Opt-out will only apply to the device and browser you are currently using, and any other devices or browsers where you have logged in.
Opt-In to the Collection and Use of Sensitive Personal Data:
Marriott does not collect Sensitive personal data, as defined under the TDPSA, unless we obtain your opt-in consent. To opt-in to the collection of precise geolocation data, please go to the settings in your mobile device/browser.
Profiling:
